President Kenyatta has gone all-out to bring his restive Mt Kenya base back to the fold.The President has also launched a political onslaught against Dr Ruto’s allies. President Kenyatta has changed tack in his campaign to popularise the Building Bridges Initiative (BBI) in Mt Kenya and counter the influence of his Deputy President William Ruto in the restive region.
The new strategy includes personally taking charge of the referendum campaigns, punishing rebel MPs, dishing out goodies to key target groups and building consensus with leaders across the political divide.



